thread.title: Anna Albano
thread.title_full: Antique Lamp Supply reviewed by Anna Albano

author: Anna Albano
title: Anna Albano
text: We've had our chandeliers for many years and after a number of moves in the armed forces, some of the crystals had seen better days. Went on their site and found almost the same pieces as came with them so many years ago in Italy. Their price point was fair as well.
